high_descs: Turn right, then turn left and head to the rack
Pick up the soap on the first level of the rack
Turn to your left and head to the sink
Put the soap on the sink then rinse it and pick it up
Turn to your right and go back to the rack
Put the soap on the second level of the rack
anns.task_desc: Put clean soap on the rack

high_descs: Move to the silver rack to the right of the sink.
Pick up the soap from the rack.
Move to the left side of the sink to the left of you.
Place the soap in the sink and run some water before turning off the water and picking up the soap.
Move to the silver rack to the right of the sink.
Place the soap on the silver rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap from the silver rack on the silver rack.

high_descs: walk to the right a bit
grab the pink bar on the shelf
walk to the left a little
put the pink bar in the sink, wash it with water, take it out
turn right, walk back to the shelf
put the pink bar on the third shelf
anns.task_desc: wash the pink bar from the shelf, put it back on the shelf

high_descs: Turn to your right, walk, and then turn left to reach the metal shelf.
Pick up a bar of soap from the top shelf.
Walk over to the sink.
Wash the soap in the sink.
Walk back over to the metal shelf.
Put the soap on the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed bar of soap on a shelf.

high_descs: Head across the room to the metal shelf that is to the right of the sink
Pick up the soap that is on the top shelf
Turn left and walk to the bathtub, then turn around and face the side of the sink
Place the soap into the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water then pick up the soap
Head to the metal shelf that is on the other side of the sink
Place the soap on the second shelf
anns.task_desc: Place a wet bar of soap on a shelf

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the rack.
Pick up the soap from the rack.
Turn left and walk to the far side of the sink.
Put the soap in the sink and fill it up with water.
Take the soap back to the rack.
Put the soap back on the rack.
